identifiers:
  - type: doi
    value: "10.5281/zenodo.15039503"
  - type: url
    value: "https://github.com/dracor-org/caldracor"

url: "https://dracor.org/cal"

abstract: >-
  CalDraCor is a TEI-encoded corpus of 205 plays by Pedro Calderón de la Barca,
  prepared for computational analysis (e.g., network and linguistic analyses),
  including scene segmentation and enriched character metadata. The corpus is
  published as part of the DraCor ecosystem and can be explored via the DraCor
  frontend.

keywords:
